It’s Mary Daniel, the pure water hawker’s 27th birthday and she has been transformed into a rare beauty for her special day’s photoshoot. The amputee, in a recent interview with the media, narrated how her ambition of becoming a lawyer was cut short due to an accident in 2006. She revealee she was the only surviving passenger on the bus. She was styled on Friday by award- winning celebrity fashion stylist, Ceoluminee to mark her birthday. The celebrity designer shared videos and images of the breathtaking look of Mary Daniel on her Instagram page as she celebrates the mother of one. Since her story went viral, the single mother of one has received huge financial support from Nigerians to better her living condition. Lagos State Government also took over her welfare.  